# Canonical line endings for all installable content. The CLI's
# canonical sha256 normalizes CRLF→LF before hashing, so source files
# must be stored as LF in git to keep `verify` deterministic across
# Windows checkouts (where core.autocrlf=true would otherwise rewrite
# line endings on checkout and produce false drift).
*.md       text eol=lf
*.json     text eol=lf
*.mdc      text eol=lf
*.ts       text eol=lf
*.js       text eol=lf
*.sh       text eol=lf

# Exclude from `git archive` tarballs (bootstrap fallback, release tarballs).
IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md export-ignore
